- Use a consistent structure for translation files to simplify management.
- Implement fallback languages for missing translations.
- Test UI components in all supported languages to ensure proper rendering.
- Allow users to set and save their language preferences in their profiles.
- Regularly update translations to keep content relevant and accurate.